705119f-a.title: Brooklyn: Jefferson Street - Broadway
705119f-a.text:
Jefferson Street, east from Broadway to Bushwick Ave. In the back-
ground, is a view of St. Mark's Evang. Litheran Church.
January 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
